Opened 2021-12-09

kitty_mod   :: Ctrl-Shift by default


Ctrl-Shift with

F2          :: Opens ~/.config/kitty/kitty.conf
F5          :: Refresh the config file

TABS
t           :: Makes a new tab
<- or ->    :: move to another tab
q           :: kill a tab

SPLITS
<Enter>     :: Makes a new split
] or [      :: Cycles through the splits
w           :: kill a split


LOCATIONS
/usr/share/doc/kitty/kitty.conf     :: originial
$HOME/.config/kitty/kitty.conf      :: user editable

KITTENS

# show a message in a tiny panel at top of screen
kitty +kitten panel sh -c 'printf "\n\n\nHello, world."; sleep 5s'

# display an image in the terminal
kitty +kitten icat $HOME/REPOS/images/00TEST/selfie.png

# themes
kitty +kittens themes
